# Power Platform Notebook - Admininstration - Reset, Restore and Clean an Environment

**Goal:** Reset, Restore and Clean a Power Platform / Dataverse environment to continue the work from a reference environment.

#!markdown

## Prerequisites check

### Power Platform CLI

#!pwsh

